Usage: get_property [-help] <var_name> <property> [-clock <clock_name>]
                    [-quiet] [-view <view_name>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<var_name>              # Specifies the single object collection
                        # (string, required)
<property>              # Specifies the property to retrieve the value
                        # (string, required)
-clock <clock_name>     # Specifies the clock for which to query certain object
                        # properties (string, optional)
-quiet                  # Specifies to exit quietly without issuing error
                        # (bool, optional)
-view <view_name>       # Specifies the analysis view in which to query the
                        # object attribute (string, optional)